    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "that's a fair point. honestly though, it feels like the people pushing these laws don't even understand how a small town works. they just see it as a way to feel good about themselves without thinking about the actual damage to the local shops. do you think there's a way to balance this without just crushing small businesses under the weight of these mandates?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
